{"tid":1396181,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Irene瀏海被剪好委屈！機場嘟嘴向粉絲告狀瘋傳","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:05:18.000Z","uid":58335,"like":19,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"73725eac0c6acde811b9bbc3ac2bd40b39b95ad2","tid":1396181,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"仙女姐姐！<br />\n<br />\nRed Velvet昨日（29日）為出席本港活動由仁川機場出發，而為下半年回歸，隊長Irene再次剪了一個空氣瀏海造型，不但顯得減齡，而且有如真人洋娃娃的美貌再次令粉絲驚艷不已。<br />\n<br />\nIrene自出道以來幾乎都是以中分或旁分的瀏海作造型，鮮有以空氣瀏海造型現身，即使有，也是十分短暫的時間。不過，Irene看來下次回歸將會持續以瀏海造型示人了！她突然以絕美的瀏海造型現身機場，長髮及腰，對著粉絲就開懷大笑，又充滿小表情。<br />\n<br />\n在通往出境的路上，Irene沿途一直接過粉絲的禮物，當有粉絲問「姐姐剪瀏海了？」，她卻嘟嘴說「被剪掉了」，臉上充滿委屈和無奈，又一度害羞地遮著自己的瀏海，十分可愛。<br />\n<br />\n網友們見到Irene好看的新Look，也紛紛留言：「因為Irene的空氣瀏海太好看，下次也想試一下」、「怎樣也漂亮」、「這美貌是真實的嗎？」、「好像洋娃娃」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190730_EN_IRENE_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190730_EN_IRENE_6.jpg&h=e311e04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190730_EN_IRENE_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190730_EN_IRENE_5.jpg&h=6d9ee7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190730_EN_IRENE_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190730_EN_IRENE_3.jpg&h=abf1ee2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190730_EN_IRENE_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190730_EN_IRENE_2.jpg&h=675beeb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br /